b'Post your full time jobs and part-time career-related positions or internships on our website, UICCAREERS.COM, a web-based system that makes job-searching easy for both students and employers.\xc2\xa0 Recruiters can self-register on that site by visiting\xc2\xa0http://www.uiccareers.com.'
b'http://www.uiccareers.com'
b'Steps For Posting Positions'
b'1) Go to\xc2\xa0www.UICcareers.com\n2) Click on Employer\n3) Click on \xe2\x80\x9cSign Up and Post Jobs\xe2\x80\x9d\n4) Follow the steps to complete company information, and click submit at the bottom of the page\n5) Wait for your confirmation email, which will arrive within 1-2 business days\n6) After receiving the confirmation email, you must log in and post your job description\n7) Your posting is usually approved within 1-2 business days; You will receive a confirmation email'
b'For more information about posting\xc2\xa0part-time jobs and internships, contact the Student Employment Office at 312-996-3130, or email\xc2\xa0studentjobs@uic.edu.'
b'studentjobs@uic.edu'
